(define circle-pts
  (map (lambda (i)
         (let ((theta (* 2 (const/pi) (/ i 8))))
           (list (geom/cos theta) (geom/sin theta))))
       (list 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7)))

(define circle-filt
  (map (lambda (r) (topo/vietoris-rips circle-pts r))
       (list 0.5 0.8 1.0 1.5 2.0 3.0)))

(define circle-pers (topo/persistence circle-filt))

circle-pers
```

[VISUAL: D3-over-canvas interactive: persistence diagram with one long-lived point in dimension 1 (the loop), others short-lived]

<!-- BUILD: run on interpreter; circle should show one persistent β₁ feature; output is the persistence data -->

